"ngram\": \"all-time\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Paris Olympics 2024: Games, results, latest updates) The 27-year-old Biles showed she was back to earn some more glittering gold medals as she laid down the marker in the all-around competition, topping the qualifying standings with a score of 59.566.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Games\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \", latest updates\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"The 27-year-old Biles\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"some more glittering gold medals\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"the marker\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around competition\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying standings\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished 1.866 points ahead of Brazil's Rebeca Andrade with reigning Olympic champion Sunisa Lee of the US in third.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9933441912593832, \"rank\": 0.006700404629745646, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"ran